channel.title: Click and Disconnect
channel.description: Ok so im using hybrid pvps source and when i open client and i have the server and everything online, i go to click somewhere it logs me out instantly and sends a error through the client loader. Idk how to fix. anyone care to tell me how to fix? Or show?

item.title: Click and Disconnect
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:

It’s a problem running the client with 64-bit java.

Download the 32-bit JRE and try again.
